    "id": "ditto-delivery-chain",
    "title": "Chasing Ghosts: A Ditto Delivery Chain",
    "summary": "Quick Assist social engineering to DLL side-loading via Ditto, malformed DNS C2, and domain compromise in under one hour.",
    "category": "DFIR",
